            <div type="transcript" id="F92A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Perhaps you'd like to buy a flower,</l>
                    <l>But I could never sell - </l>
                    <l>If you would like to <em>borrow,</em> </l>
                    <l>Until the Daffodil </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Unties her yellow Bonnet</l>
                    <l>Beneath the village door, </l>
                    <l>Until the Bees, from Clover rows </l>
                    <l>Their Hock, and sherry, draw, </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Why, I will lend until just then, </l>
                    <l>But not an hour more!</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
